Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:10.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:12.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,比我想的还要大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:17.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,古代都市巴比伦过去是非常繁荣的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:20.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这里留下了各种各样的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:24.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,像连接死后的世界有恶魔住在这里诸如此类
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:28.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也流传跟地上一样的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:30.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么入口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:35.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有四处这四根柱子都有各自的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:37.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但只有一条路能通向巴别
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:42.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,前提是这张在古董店买回来的地图是真品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:47.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,古代文字吗  上面写了什么艾尔乔亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:50.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  应该是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:57.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,火之神祝融所守护的南之门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:01.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从那个塔进去应该不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.91,0:01:13.45,geci,,0,0,0,,在这流失了爱的城市中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:18.38,geci,,0,0,0,,那正在微笑的你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:28.97,geci,,0,0,0,,用足以扼杀孤独的力量  紧紧拥抱我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.64,0:01:37.27,geci,,0,0,0,,被束缚的Limit  解放它回归本始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.31,0:01:39.35,geci,,0,0,0,,纵燃燃殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:49.66,geci,,0,0,0,,也要在这渲染了艳丽的夜之尽头翩然起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.74,0:01:53.53,geci,,0,0,0,,就让它烙印于灵魂之上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:02:03.30,geci,,0,0,0,,来吧  尽情闪耀吧  眼前的你  昳丽无双
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:10.14,geci,,0,0,0,,在这夜之尽头  翩然起舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:14.18,geci,,0,0,0,,就让它烙印于灵魂之上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:22.10,geci,,0,0,0,,来吧  尽情闪耀吧  眼前的你  昳丽无双
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:25.48,geci,,0,0,0,,飞扬而上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:30.78,geci,,0,0,0,,在这流失了爱的城市中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:43.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你说要找门的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:46.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但连长什么样都不清楚要怎么找
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:48.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米特里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:50.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:51.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是钥匙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:52.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:05.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:11.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,第11话深处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:15.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这应该是通向巴别的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:17.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:17.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:19.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜霞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:26.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这前方是巴别的话  很可能设置了陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:29.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:30.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:32.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没有跟你讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:34.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:48.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这些脚印还很新
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:50.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是德尔扎因他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是被捷足先登了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:56.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不快一点就糟了  下一扇门呢  在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:57.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:00.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只能爬上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:01.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:04.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:08.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在还要攀岩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:09.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,攀岩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:13.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对了法拉利昂  能再变大一次载我们上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:16.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,别强龙所难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:17.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:35.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  你不用担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:44.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:49.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:55.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:56.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:58.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,托你的福得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:04:59.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:02.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我说托你的福得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:04.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  这样不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:08.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  那边两个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:10.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,别磨磨蹭蹭了  快点爬上来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:17.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,终于爬上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要安心还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:22.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,爬完墙接下来是迷宫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,尽是些麻烦的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:31.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:33.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我清楚的说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:52.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不打算杀死德尔扎因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:57.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经召集了祖乌族岛和偏僻地方的士兵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:02.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没错但是我期待的是光荣革命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我知道但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:06.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:10.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙  你真的觉得能和德尔扎因沟通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:16.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知他为王的作风但为人是怎样我就不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:18.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他恶贯满盈除此之外你还想知道什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:23.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他死了的话祖乌族和那些贫苦的人都能得以拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:30.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要为解决国家问题把王…把人杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:36.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,召集士兵只是为了迫使德尔扎因让出王位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你想要杀死王呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:48.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂你连理由都不说就想要我们帮你未免也太自私了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:50.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你也该说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:54.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:07:02.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,德尔扎因并不是我父亲他把我身为前任国王的父亲给杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:09.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要肩负起这份深仇大恨发誓为了报仇要变得更强而现在机会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:15.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇吗  我的革命也是复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:20.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我的一位祖乌族朋友因激怒贵族而被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:26.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了向那个贵族复仇去磨砺自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:31.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在经历人生百态之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我意识到那不是一条正确的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:37.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算血流满地也不能改变什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.61,0:07:41.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了那贵族的话他身边的人又会为了复仇而来追杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:45.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,结果产生的不过就是冤冤相报罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:50.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我选择了向这腐朽的世界复仇这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:52.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,以革命的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:57.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次与你见面问你的问题我再问你一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:01.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果打倒了王之后你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,面对没有王的国度你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:11.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说最先和德尔扎因交涉的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:17.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的谈话结束之前你绝对不能向那家伙拔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:21.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我只渴望能够复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:22.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:34.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:36.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  王子殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:40.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在拔剑相向之前先与他沟通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:52.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要走过这个迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:54.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就能找到前往巴别塔的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:57.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我不觉得会这么顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:09:00.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我会保护迪米特里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:01.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,别一遍一遍地说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:02.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要你多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:04.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:18.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米特里奥他们差不多也该进入巴别了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:21.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他们能平安到达巴别塔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:23.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人肯定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:27.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何  我们必须要整备部队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:35.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:37.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家集合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:40.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米特里奥…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:51.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,洞察大地  聆听风语
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:53.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:05.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,周围弥漫着令人不适的瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:08.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只能沿着这条路继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:21.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,终于至此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:25.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无论发生什么  身处何方我都会遵从迪米特里奥的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:26.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:30.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我会用生命保护迪米特里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:37.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:40.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米里奥没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:41.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:44.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米特里奥好像说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:45.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬  太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:51.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哎什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:54.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们到了巴别塔以后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:55.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你就能回到地上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:57.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:02.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊我到达巴比伦的时候明明那么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:04.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么现在却
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:06.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:08.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,喂艾米里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:12.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:14.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那个我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:17.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要到巴别塔了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:20.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说…我想应该能够回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:23.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前还和你有约定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:26.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那个约定仍然有效吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:28.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我想再确认一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:31.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,说重点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:33.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说你是不量还想报…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:33.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,走出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:43.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那个应该就是去巴别塔的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:47.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,喂等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:57.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到你们的葬身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:58.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是埋伏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,王子先从你开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:18.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:26.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该告诉过你不能杀王子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:29.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是吓唬他而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:32.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,又是你啊  真是烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你们没话可说快路开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:41.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有我们有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:45.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:47.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,来的比我预想的要快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:51.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这正说明你已经时曰无多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:52.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讽刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:54.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个性急的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:57.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这场战斗很快就会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:12:59.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是倒下的人只会是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:03.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我是狼斗组的基特罗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:06.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,名字已经无关紧要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:49.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我得好好地一尽地主之谊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:52.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让你们尝尝和这伤□一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:55.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不比这伤□更为深刻的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我要撕碎你们的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:01.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,把你们的肉一片片割下来  慢慢玩弄至死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:37.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了 乖乖投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:52.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:59.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,王说过  不能杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:00.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:01.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是自己的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:04.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,居然放过一个时刻想取自己性命的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:08.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,德尔扎因王还真是天真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:10.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:34.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:40.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是打架的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:47.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙德尔扎因马上就要到这来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:51.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:53.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:00.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,休想过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:13.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:14.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:21.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,敢碍我的事  可是要吃苦头的快让开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:22.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不我不会让开的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:28.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我的化宝具就算不能打倒你留住你还是办得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:44.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是那么肆意妄为啊 伊贝尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:47.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见啊露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:49.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:52.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:57.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙身上可是留着祖乌族的血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:17:01.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从一开始就没心思跟你们玩革命游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:02.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:06.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,露易丝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:08.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,革命反正也改变不了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:13.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我身上的一半的血是祖乌族的血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:17.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是靠着这副外表我能作为ENDORA人活到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:20.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也从未受到歧视
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:24.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我对这样的世界一直抱有疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:31.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲擅长制药母亲擅长缝纫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:35.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他们没有发挥长处的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:38.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅因为父亲是祖乌族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:43.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而母亲则因嫁给了令人忌讳的祖乌族男人为由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:47.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都只能做ENDORA人从来不屑于做的苦力劳动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:51.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是孩子的时候 已经觉得这一定是哪里出错了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:58.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以与迪米特里奥的志向产生共鸣而加入伊格纳茨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:00.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你还说着那种蠢话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:02.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是钱啊  钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:05.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了活下去我需要钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:07.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要把我与你们混为一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:12.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,把伊格纳茨的行踪告诉狠斗组就能拿到钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:15.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来就能让父母从繁重劳役中解脱出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:19.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,革命是有闲心的人去做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:22.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,动手  露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:27.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了艾尔乔亚你真的很傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:28.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:30.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,迪米特里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:34.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,比起艾尔乔亚我的赏金更高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:36.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:41.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么革命军啊连同伴背叛了也察觉不到的蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:42.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:45.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我被小瞧了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:50.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊你是狠斗组的同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:57.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的行踪完全暴露了特别是那位王子加入我们之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:01.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我将队伍缩小了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:03.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,最初我也是半信半疑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:06.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在这里遭遇了狠斗组的埋伏之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:08.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就确信无疑了啊露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:19.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,给我认真点啊迪米特里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:21.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是要杀了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:24.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,即使那样也无所谓露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:25.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:25.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:25.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:27.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,果然这是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:28.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:31.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会帮你复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:34.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这副鬼叫我还以为你想到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:35.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:36.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:37.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:40.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,跟迪米特里奥所说一样先和他谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:44.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,喂艾米里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:49.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心情你怎么能了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:50.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:54.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不了解你的心情完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:58.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是复仇那种事我认为是错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:06.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:07.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:09.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:12.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:17.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:18.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:20.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个必须阻止艾米里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:27.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.34,0:20:29.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就可以启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:34.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,由于巴别塔的门开放有时间限制
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:36.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,开门之后还请尽快行动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:45.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这下多年以来的夙愿就能实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:46.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,德尔扎因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:55.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:13.56,geci,,0,0,0,,兜兜转转   迂迂回回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:21.65,geci,,0,0,0,,时至今日的种种  成就了今天的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.77,0:21:28.49,geci,,0,0,0,,go my way    go my way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:48.76,geci,,0,0,0,,世界轮回   将从未见过的未来映照于青空之上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:57.48,geci,,0,0,0,,超越过去超越自我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:22:04.69,geci,,0,0,0,,希望今天能以欣欣笑颜出现在你的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:09.95,geci,,0,0,0,,要聊点什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:18.12,geci,,0,0,0,,夏日的清香纠缠着心灵的悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.66,0:22:29.05,geci,,0,0,0,,难以言喻的情感只为传达那一句  喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:43.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.74,0:22:44.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,巴别塔之光
